===============================
octopus
===============================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/octopus.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/octopus

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/benzid-wael/octopus.svg
        :target: https://travis-ci.org/benzid-wael/octopus

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/octopus/badge/?version=latest
        :target: https://readthedocs.org/projects/octopus/?badge=latest
